{
  "text": "Firms that use direct export channels can also improve their stock of existing resources by accessing information and knowledge on foreign markets. Firms that establish direct export channels have access to valuable information and knowledge about foreign markets, such as the different national market regulations, alternative tastes and client preferences, distribution chains, and external management practices [CITATION_1] .",
